{"tid":2119921,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(順產科) 人氣曾力壓宋慧喬！童星長大淪「脫星」…跨男人身上胸任揉","createTime":"2020-07-22T11:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T11:50:15.000Z","uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71eb540093b404f6d0c8da0a279f55a343fdbfd6","tid":2119921,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"呢度有幾多人睇過<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/15/2455970-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2F2455970-XXL.jpg&h=34fdb37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年最知名的經典韓劇《順風婦產科》是不少台灣人入門的基本作品，其中更藏著不少大咖明星，如最知名的宋慧喬、朴美善、李泰蘭等人，至今都在演藝圈相當活躍。然而最有名的不得不提「小霸王」美月，不管做什麼事都讓人又愛又恨，甚至名聲一度超越宋慧喬。沒想到長大後的她卻慘淪脫星。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/05/24/1373056-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F1373056-XXL.jpg&h=6f8ac788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/15/2455975-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2F2455975-XXL.jpg&h=ac5ec46b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飾演「美月」的金成恩，長大後變了許多。（圖／翻攝自IG、推特）<br />\n<br />\n美月本名金成恩，現年已經27歲的她，據悉當年因為太早嚐到走紅滋味，讓她的人生一路相當顛簸，24歲那年，她遭到霸凌嫌棄長太醜而罹患憂鬱症，為此，金成恩砸下68萬台幣「進廠維修」，最後成功擺脫嬰兒肥的臉蛋，長相大升級。讓人驚訝的是，她為了撕掉童星的陰影，接下成人電影重要主角《花樣女鬼》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/15/2455973-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2F2455973-XXL.jpg&h=4363618b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金成恩曾為了電影有大尺度裸露。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n在電影中她不僅模樣嫵媚，更是有大尺度的脱戲，跨坐在男人身上脫掉BRA之外，還讓男人任意蹂躪，讓不少粉絲看傻了眼，直呼過去的美月已經消失了。不過金成恩反而沒有退縮，還在自己的推特上發聲，直言自己不需要同情「這完全是我的選擇」無奈作品播出後沒紅，她則改轉當直播主，希望力拚再次翻紅的機會。<br />\n<br />\n又係童星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295a5031e82777dd15c4341c37c0ebd1071f9f23","tid":2119921,"uid":255687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"呢套當年成日睇 幾好笑"},{"pid":"5e3042113397b36516ee25c42a6550b063297c90","tid":2119921,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"順風婦產科係幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593712f9b17392c1a8c6dd81c93592586381fbf8","tid":2119921,"uid":70977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"係咪即係之前拍過滋味行個個？"},{"pid":"468b375e053126ff2d9003c781c5e6e3633a38f0","tid":2119921,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"seed?"},{"pid":"ac6e94d0a6cfb5996041f156813cfb05be883ed0","tid":2119921,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e3042113397b36516ee25c42a6550b063297c90","tid":2119921,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"順風婦產科係幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:48:14.000Z","msg":"當年無乜娛樂<br />\n睇呢啲可以笑一日"},{"pid":"9cb4d35a8f94fa3ef58b4398730ce99d0ad17981","tid":2119921,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"佢老豆好好笑"}]}